<br>
Now, I for one see a perfect and natural solution for implementing this.  As it stands now, MA armor does not include Gloves.  So, why not make a line of MA Armor Gloves that does the different damage types?  This will not only help to complete the armor set but will also make non-weapon wielding MA's a bit more viable.  Because Funcom, not all MA's want to wield weapons and we resent your forcing us!<br>
<br>
